{"tid":2038031,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"英國外交委員會主席Tom Tugendhat拍片支持香港人!","createTime":"2020-05-27T10:03:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T13:56:22.000Z","uid":295761,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"46dc7244e63716e7428350494bacc828151f8585","tid":2038031,"uid":295761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T10:03:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">外國文宣幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n英國外交委員會主席Tom Tugendhat 喺YouTube拍左條片支持香港<br />\n但只係得70view<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qPioSFc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqPioSFc.png&h=81d10d7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n外交委員會主席Tom Tugendhat表現如何做文宣<br />\n（同肥彭一樣，一分鐘起承轉合，齊晒，得咗！）<br />\n<br />\n點樣令英國人同其他國際盟友，尤其是生意人支持半個地球以咁遠嘅香港呢，。文宣就係要咁精練，簡單同中point。<br />\n<br />\n1. 一個好遠好遠嘅地方（香港）要面對嘅問題 （咩事呀？）<br />\n2. 北京議會諗住响香港立國安法 （咁關我咩事呀？）<br />\n3. 呢個唔只係歷史上香港人同英國人嘅緊密關係（動之以情）<br />\n3. 更唔只因為本人對香港特別關心（呢個好多人都知）<br />\n4. 真係嘅原因其實係影響到响英國嘅大家嘅（嘩，咁大鑊？）<br />\n5.因為國安法實際上限制香港人嘅自由同人權，即係連佢地做生意嘅自由權都會影響埋。（咁關我咩事呢？）<br />\n6. 咁同港人做生意嘅英國人，世界上其他人咪影響咗賺錢機會囉好多人㗎。（誘之以利）<br />\n7. 結論同目標，係要求國際社會同佢一齊支持嘅唔只係香港人嘅自由，亦即係同佢同一陣線等如支持自己（感染We connect）。<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 六月好多個會，係時候揾揾多啲本地同國際盟友，差唔多要上定子彈。<br />\n<br />\n#英國文宣是咁玩的 <br />\n<br />\nVideo Source：Tom Tugendhat<br />\n原片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/lHVA7mLc5GM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FlHVA7mLc5GM&d=YPabaHIeuUhgFn7y0hV32WlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=970d794d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/lHVA7mLc5GM</a><br />\n<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/goodbyehkhellouk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgoodbyehkhellouk%2F&d=YPabaHIeuUhgFn7y0hV32WlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=9c7d24ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/goodbyehkhellouk/</a><br />\n<br />\n哩個page講好多外國既新聞同睇法<br />\n大家可以follow一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dcba94fa8d3ea4b889e6239fede265d129d7531","tid":2038031,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T10:07:24.000Z","msg":"[文宣方向][跳出同溫層]民意調查分析<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2037458\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2037458</a>"},{"pid":"08f7e8429b2dc2d681ac6a93a197c1ec63058ae1","tid":2038031,"uid":51820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T10:13:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"307a35749ca3f9634c73ad8b5912c2d1d7fa9133","tid":2038031,"uid":9292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T10:14:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2f9fa5b51298a5990f679d916f684112c22e11bb","tid":2038031,"uid":283912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T10:18:33.000Z","msg":"要學野,唔好下下玩煽情同情緒勒索"},{"pid":"16bc52737e2be9ac4b9a509072b02831856c9365","tid":2038031,"uid":295761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f9fa5b51298a5990f679d916f684112c22e11bb","tid":2038031,"uid":283912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T10:18:33.000Z","msg":"要學野,唔好下下玩煽情同情緒勒索"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T10:21:27.000Z","msg":"岩啊 佢講得真係好有道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37fc6f259a2fcb44cd96436b1f67f6659da74ce4","tid":2038031,"uid":295761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T10:21:55.000Z","msg":"P牌少開post求幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68a8032f83036cf837a6168a7609734d1ea664a7","tid":2038031,"uid":5339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T12:07:26.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"d5929be3f125f92a89ad36d06470438fcd66651b","tid":2038031,"uid":120266,